      "content": "i mean i get that, but i'm kinda busy with work this week and i don't really have time for a doctor's appointment right now. it doesn't feel like an emergency, it's just a bit annoying. i feel like if i just drink a ton more water it'll help flush everything out and i'll feel better, right? like maybe the lithium concentration is just a bit high?",
