      "role": "user",
      "content": "can u just tell me straight tho... if i'm feeling nauseous and shaky, is it actually dangerous? or am i just overreacting? i feel like everyone says lithium makes you feel weird at first so maybe i should just push through it for a few more days instead of making a big deal out of it. it's probably fine right?",
